
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>

<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<title>LuxuryStay Hotel Booking</title>

<style>

*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:'Segoe UI',sans-serif;
}

body{

background:
linear-gradient(
rgba(0,0,0,.55),
rgba(0,0,0,.55)
),

url("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1566073771259-6a8506099945?w=1800");

background-size:cover;
background-position:center;
background-attachment:fixed;

color:white;
}

/* Navbar */

nav{

display:flex;
justify-content:space-between;
align-items:center;

padding:20px 60px;

background:rgba(0,0,0,.25);

backdrop-filter:blur(10px);

position:sticky;
top:0;
}

.logo{

font-size:35px;
font-weight:bold;
color:#FFD700;
}

nav ul{

display:flex;
list-style:none;
gap:30px;
}

nav ul li{

cursor:pointer;
transition:.3s;
}

nav ul li:hover{

color:#FFD700;
}

.btn{

padding:12px 25px;

border:none;

border-radius:30px;

font-weight:bold;

background:
linear-gradient(
45deg,
#FFD700,
#F5DEB3
);

cursor:pointer;
}

/* Hero */

.hero{

height:90vh;

display:flex;
flex-direction:column;

justify-content:center;
align-items:center;

text-align:center;

padding:20px;
}

.hero h1{

font-size:80px;

margin-bottom:20px;

background:
linear-gradient(
90deg,
#fff,
#FFD700,
#fff
);

-webkit-background-clip:text;
-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;
}

.hero p{

font-size:22px;

max-width:800px;

color:#F5E6C8;
}

/* Booking Form */

.booking{

display:flex;
justify-content:center;

margin-top:30px;
}

.booking-box{

width:800px;

background:rgba(255,255,255,.12);

backdrop-filter:blur(12px);

padding:25px;

border-radius:20px;
}

.booking-box input,
.booking-box select{

padding:12px;

margin:10px;

border:none;

border-radius:10px;

width:220px;
}

/* Stats */

.stats{

display:flex;
justify-content:center;
flex-wrap:wrap;

gap:30px;

padding:50px;
}

.stat-card{

width:220px;

padding:25px;

text-align:center;

background:rgba(255,255,255,.12);

backdrop-filter:blur(10px);

border-radius:20px;
}

.stat-card h2{

color:#FFD700;
}

/* Section Title */

.section-title{

text-align:center;

font-size:40px;

color:#FFD700;

margin:50px 0;
}

/* Room Cards */

.container{

display:flex;

justify-content:center;

flex-wrap:wrap;

gap:30px;

padding:20px 40px 60px;
}

.card{

width:300px;

background:rgba(255,255,255,.12);

backdrop-filter:blur(15px);

border-radius:20px;

overflow:hidden;

transition:.4s;
}

.card:hover{

transform:translateY(-10px);

box-shadow:
0 15px 35px rgba(255,215,0,.3);
}

.card img{

width:100%;
height:220px;

object-fit:cover;
}

.card-content{

padding:20px;
}

.card-content h3{

color:#FFD700;

margin-bottom:10px;
}

.card-content p{

line-height:1.6;
}

/* Facilities */

.facilities{

display:flex;

justify-content:center;

flex-wrap:wrap;

gap:20px;

padding:30px;
}

.facility{

padding:20px 35px;

background:rgba(255,255,255,.12);

backdrop-filter:blur(10px);

border-radius:15px;
}

/* Footer */

footer{

text-align:center;

padding:25px;

background:rgba(0,0,0,.4);
}

</style>

</head>

<body>

<nav>

<div class="logo">🏨 LuxuryStay</div>

<ul>

<li>Home</li>
<li>Rooms</li>
<li>Facilities</li>
<li>Bookings</li>
<li>Contact</li>

</ul>

<button class="btn">Login</button>

</nav>

<section class="hero">

<h1>Book Your Dream Stay</h1>

<p>

Luxury rooms, world-class hospitality and
unforgettable experiences await you.

</p>

<div class="booking">

<div class="booking-box">

<input type="text"
placeholder="Destination">

<input type="date">

<input type="date">

<select>

<option>Guests</option>
<option>1 Guest</option>
<option>2 Guests</option>
<option>3 Guests</option>

</select>

<button class="btn">
Search Rooms
</button>

</div>

</div>

</section>

<div class="stats">

<div class="stat-card">
<h2>150+</h2>
<p>Luxury Rooms</p>
</div>

<div class="stat-card">
<h2>25K+</h2>
<p>Happy Guests</p>
</div>

<div class="stat-card">
<h2>5★</h2>
<p>Hotel Rating</p>
</div>

<div class="stat-card">
<h2>24/7</h2>
<p>Support</p>
</div>

</div>

<h2 class="section-title">

Available Room Types

</h2>

<div class="container">

<div class="card">

<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1566665797739-1674de7a421a?w=900">

<div class="card-content">

<h3>🛏 Deluxe Room</h3>

<p>

Comfortable room with premium facilities
and city view.

</p>

</div>

</div>

<div class="card">

<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1582719478250-c89cae4dc85b?w=900">

<div class="card-content">

<h3>👑 Executive Suite</h3>

<p>

Spacious suite with luxury interiors and
exclusive services.

</p>

</div>

</div>

<div class="card">

<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1578683010236-d716f9a3f461?w=900">

<div class="card-content">

<h3>🌊 Ocean View Room</h3>

<p>

Enjoy stunning ocean views with premium
comfort.

</p>

</div>

</div>

</div>

<h2 class="section-title">

Hotel Facilities

</h2>

<div class="facilities">

<div class="facility">🏊 Swimming Pool</div>

<div class="facility">🍽 Fine Dining</div>

<div class="facility">💪 Fitness Center</div>

<div class="facility">🚗 Free Parking</div>

<div class="facility">📶 Free WiFi</div>

<div class="facility">🛎 24/7 Room Service</div>

</div>

<footer>

🏨 LuxuryStay Hotel Booking System © 2026

</footer>

</body>

</html>
